Classified-Ads-Script

License:        GPL v3
Installation:   http://classified-ads-script.co.uk
Support at:     http://classified-ads-script.co.uk/forum/

Requirements:

Apache 2
PHP 5.3+ (GD support)
MySql 5+

Installation:

1. Download and unzip the package.
2. Create a database for the script on your web server, as well as a MySQL user who has all privileges for accessing and modifying it.
3. Run the sql command are found in the db-install.sql file in your database and optionally for sample data, do the same with the db-sample.sql
3. Open the config.php file in the admin/include directory in a text editor and fill in your details following the comments in the file
4. Upload all files in the desired location on your web server
5. That's it, all done!
